591
00:28:05,079 --> 00:28:06,599
You knocked me down!

592
00:28:06,599 --> 00:28:07,800
Everyone, you saw what happened!

593
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:09,479
Give me ten taels of silver

594
00:28:09,479 --> 00:28:10,599
