595
00:28:10,959 --> 00:28:12,000
All of you, dismiss!

596
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:13,640
What's going on?

597
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:14,839
Officers!

598
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,800
Officers, my legs!

599
00:28:16,800 --> 00:28:17,439
Are you alright?

600
