602
00:28:20,199 --> 00:28:20,839
She knocked me down.

603
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,640
My legs!

604
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:24,920
Stop right there!

605
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,479
Stop!

